        public NPC GetStartingNPCInstance()
        Reads and instantiates a new starting npc for this quest. It's common practice to only call this method a single time, as you only need one copy of 'earl' who people talk to to give the quest.

      • instanceQuest

        public Quest instanceQuest(Participant participant)
                    throws org.bukkit.configuration.InvalidConfigurationException,
                           SessionConflictException
        Returns the complete Quest this configuration represents. Subsequent calls to this method return new instances of the represented quest. It is up to the caller to keep track of returned quests and optimize performance when simply needing a reference to previously-instantiated Quests
        Returns:
        A new quest instance
        Throws:
        org.bukkit.configuration.InvalidConfigurationException
